{"tid":1219842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘現況！","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:39:53.000Z","uid":578,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad208772f0e1648b0bd5a86c5b0d28862d8de48","tid":1219842,"uid":578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeX3mq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeX3mq6.jpg&h=59ac0b7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pcYiajs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpcYiajs.jpg&h=53148b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n重有人唱緊聖詩，得閒可以出黎支持"},{"pid":"ede9aec6f94adb6f359c5d8f48a11f8596fb5e6d","tid":1219842,"uid":224860,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:30:41.000Z","msg":"基本上大部分前線警察都係欺善怕惡<br />\n記住自己應有嘅權利<br />\n睇下呢條影片就知 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/gkv36k14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fgkv36k14&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=ab4aab69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/gkv36k14</a><br />\n專恰後生仔 千祈唔好俾佢兇到 <br />\n根本無野好驚 要冷靜<br />\n<br />\n(1)警察有權查身分證<br />\n向15歲或以上之香港居民查閱身分證<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果查你身分證或護照,你照俾佢,無問題 但你有權保持緘默,即係只要向警方提供個人姓名及住址(ONLY區) ,其他都可以唔答<br />\n<br />\n(2)警察搜身<br />\n根據《警隊條例》（第232章）第54(2)條，警察頂要有合理懷疑必須根據事實情況而作出客觀判斷先可以搜物<br />\n警務人員不可以向異性進行搜身。 如要向一位女性搜身，而當時沒有女警在場，該女子便應被帶到最就近的警署，由女警為她進行搜身。<br />\n<br />\n(3)你有權用電話影住警察,用電話影呀SIR係要保障自己, 香港從沒有市民因拍下警察照片而被定罪的情況，以一般拍攝而言，理論上亦不涉襲警，故市民無需擔心。<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"31cae9e9ec3fe411a18b88818d51ef1b5319531a","tid":1219842,"uid":170135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101a71ca3aabad37658d2be7c9a96a2299aac180","tid":1219842,"uid":190954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b70ec7b49f10fed49ec856f4a8d490fe82ddfea1","tid":1219842,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:15.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝你地"},{"pid":"bfb7e0484e69558efd56232240303fade5bef945","tid":1219842,"uid":60423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"31cae9e9ec3fe411a18b88818d51ef1b5319531a","tid":1219842,"uid":170135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:46.000Z","msg":"真心好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好堅持好搏<br />\n我已經頂唔順要休息<br />\n係現場個精神壓力大到仆街"},{"pid":"a19dc3ff48aca4d9ae0497fdcf7ac3e3b56ca36d","tid":1219842,"uid":82853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:33:49.000Z","msg":"加油，晏d接力！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ef0f3dcd49c81fd2de5e026fbb539faafb3213","tid":1219842,"uid":44367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:35:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TtQ9hwYoyWQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTtQ9hwYoyWQ&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=dad4eb0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TtQ9hwYoyWQ</a><br />\n<br />\n加油啊耶撚！"},{"pid":"281dc0ebb9a09e9277fb53a476b625b28e56606b","tid":1219842,"uid":140538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pi